<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>أخرجه ابن صاعد <span class="c2">(٦)</span> وابن حبان <span class="c2">(٤١٧١)</span><a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
